🔋8X Thick Tinned Copper Core: AINOPE usb c to usb c charging cable has the newly upgraded 8-core thick tinned copper core wire body, compared with 60W and 3.1A charging cables, the charging efficiency is increased by 88%, and the charging stability is increased by 93%.

🔋10X Durable, Never Rupture & Break: The length of 6.6 ft USB C cable is fit for home/work or play together. There is no need to sit next to the plug anymore. Type C to type c cable has professional electronic safety certifications. The SR anti-break design and durable double braiding enhance the robustness of the cable. Through 40,000+ bending tests, we ensure AINOPE 100W usbc to usbc fast charging cable has longer service life and never breaks.

🔋Doing Responsibly and Sustainably🔋: As a responsible company, AINOPE operates sustainably, to high environmental and social standards. We continue to embed sustainability ever deeper in the way we do business – in our own operations and beyond, together with our suppliers. AINOPE has focus on making USB cables for over 10 years. We sincerely hope that you can like our product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Highly recommend! Can't praise them enough!
reviews.reviewText: Great quality! 6ft long and the 90° plug end is really nice feature. Keeps the cord out of the way while holding it in your hand and supports fast and super fast charging. Ordered 4 would definitely reorder if needed!Update- After 6 months of HARD use and the new puppy chewing on one of them, they're hands down some of the nicest and well built charging cords I've ever owned! They handle fast data transfer and fast charge my Samsung s23+ even at the Super fast rate! They go from the house, to the garage, to the truck, and back all the time. Not a single problem! I highly recommend not only these cords but this company and all their cords. They look and feel nice in the hand and are almost bulletproof! For the price point if you don't pick some up, you are making a mistake. I just picked up 3 more cords from this manufacturer for a new car stereo install.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Loving these cables!
reviews.reviewText: These cables are super! The fact that I got them on sale really cheap is a big bonus. I have only had them a few weeks but I have had zero issues. They charge quickly and I love the right angle connection. Some people complain that the cable it took stuff and although it is stiffer than other cables I've used, it doesn't bother me. They are sufficiently flexible. And unlike the super flexible cables I've bought recently, these have shown no sings of fraying or wearing down at all.

reviews.reviewTitle: Very durable and quick to charge
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this 2-pack because of how quickly our son (5-years) goes through cords. So far, after almost regular daily use, he hasn’t managed to wreck the first cord out of the package.Usually, the first thing to go on a cord in our house is the cord’s ability to remain plugged into either the charger block or the iPad. The connections on both ends of this cord remain tight and reliable.Having the bend in one end of the cord means that you don’t have to worry about wrecking the end of the cord that plugs into your device. With the bend, the cord is safely “tucked” out of the way when the device rests on your lap or any other surface.
充電中にスマホを使うときに手に当たらず使えるのは良いと思います。
